title: Kubernetes: Ingresses
agents: kubernetes
catalog: containerization/kubernetes
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors path, port, and service name of ingresses.

 It makes it possible to identify vanishing or newly
 instantiated ingresses.  It is always {OK}.

 Use Check HTTP service to monitor the state of the services
 behind the ingresses.

item:
 Backend of the ingress

inventory:
 One service is created for each path.

